Research In Motion Appointed as Sponsor of Rugby World Cup in New Zealand

-- B y   D a n   B a y n e s
-- 
2011-04-18T01:25:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-18/research-in-motion-appointed-as-sponsor-of-rugby-world-cup-in-new-zealand.html
Research In Motion Ltd. (RIM)  was today
appointed as a sponsor of the 2011 Rugby World Cup, the
International Rugby Board said.  Under the agreement, RIM’s BlackBerry smartphone will be
the official handheld mobile device of the Sept. 9-Oct. 23
tournament in  New Zealand . Financial terms of the sponsorship
weren’t given in a release from the Dublin-based IRB.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Baynes at 
 dbaynes@bloomberg.net  